## Delegate Response Contract

Every sub-agent MUST return upon completion:

```
FILES_CHANGED: [list of files created/modified]
SUMMARY: [what was done in 1-2 sentences]
LOCAL_VALIDATION: [lint, tests and/or build results]
EXTERNAL_DEPENDENCIES: [changes needed in other modules, or "none"]
```

